txt.en:
'Mae govannen. I am in need of your assistance in completing a series of missions for the on-going efforts to preserve the Wildwood.

'The factions of Free Peoples exploring the wilds have treated the woods well, but there are many others who seek to burn and lay waste to the pristine beauty of the Wildwood. The forest is vast and the number of Free Peoples here is few. Much is needed to be done.

'Would you assist me by completing several of these missions?'
Radhril can be found in Trestlebridge.\n\nYou should talk to Radhril.
Those vying for resources in the Wildwood of Bree-land are in need of assistance.
Radhril can be found in Trestlebridge.\n\nYou should complete missions in the Wildwood.
'I thank you for your assistance. Your good deeds shall help keep the Wildwood a place of beauty and calm in Bree-land.'
